>与歌剧歌手玛丽娜·维奥蒂。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/celine-dion">席琳·迪翁 (Celine Dion)</a>也是四年来首次演出，自<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/celine-dion-reveals-stiff-person-syndrome-diagnosis-reschedules-and-cancels-shows-3363354">2022 年透露自己被诊断出患有僵人综合症 (SPS) 以来，她在首场演出中演绎了伊迪丝·琵雅芙 (Edith Piaf) 的《L&#39;Hymne A L&#39;Amour》。</a></p><p>现在，巴黎奥运会将于今晚（8 月 11 日）闭幕，据悉 Eilish、Snoop 和 Red Hot Chilli Peppers 将在此次活动中表演，这象征着奥运火炬将移交给洛杉矶。安吉利斯。这三人都来自这座城市，而奥运会将于 2028 年举办。</p><p>洛杉矶同胞。作为仪式的一部分，本土<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/h-e-r">HER</a>还将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/h-e-r-to-perform-us-national-anthem-at-paris-olympics-closing-ceremony-3782550">在法兰西体育场现场演唱美国国歌</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3750569" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3750569" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3750569" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Billie-Eilish@2000x1270-1.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Billie-Eilish@2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Billie-Eilish@2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Billie-Eilish@2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Billie-Eilish@2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Billie-Eilish@2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Billie-Eilish@2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3750569" class="wp-caption-text">比莉·艾利什于 2024 年 3 月 10 日出席由拉迪卡·琼斯在加利福尼亚州比佛利山庄沃利斯·安纳伯格表演艺术中心主办的 2024 年名利场奥斯卡派对。 （摄影：Karwai Tang/WireImage/Getty Images）</figcaption></figure><p> LA28 主席 Casey Wasserman 在一份声明中宣布了表演者名单，他表示：“这是 LA28 历史上迄今为止最重要的时刻，奥林匹克旗帜从巴黎传递到洛杉矶。”</p><p>他继续说道：“我们很高兴能与当地艺术家一起展示洛杉矶最优秀的作品，并感谢 Billie、HER、Chili Peppers 和 Snoop 的合作，这将是一场为全球观众带来的精彩演出，让粉丝们有机会领略其中的魅力2028 年将会发生什么。”</p><p>艾利什通过她的 Instagram 证实了这一消息，并在故事中写道，她对表演感到“非常兴奋”。在宣布这一消息之前，人们猜测<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/charli-xcx">Charli XCX</a>将与这位歌手一起登台，此前她在本周早些时候预告了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-billie-eilish-guess-remix-the-dare-finneas-3780251">两人的新合作单曲“Guess”</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/olympics-2024-charli-xcx-teases-performance-with-billie-eilish-at-closing-ceremony-3782329">潜在表演</a>。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C-gkpyAy1Xs/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.65